138
00:13:16,200 --> 00:13:17,020
But look!

139
00:13:17,120 --> 00:13:17,940
It's grey.

140
00:13:18,040 --> 00:13:20,400
And look at this.
This stain's been washed in.

141
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:22,640
If you want really white whites,

142
00:13:22,760 --> 00:13:25,120
try Vanish Oxi
Action Crystal White.

143
00:13:25,280 --> 00:13:28,400
One scoop and you see
the difference in just one wash.

144
00:13:28,560 --> 00:13:30,960
Look what it's doing
in your machine.

145
00:13:31,120 --> 00:13:32,500
Drop your stain
over this.

146
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,020
Look at it go!

147
00:13:34,120 --> 00:13:35,060
This is good!

148
00:13:35,160 --> 00:13:36,140
And it's perfect

149
00:13:36,240 --> 00:13:37,460
for all your
washable whites.

150
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:38,700
She was right.

151
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:40,800
Vanish Oxi Action Crystal White.

152
