153
00:16:40,970 --> 00:16:43,790
We could say it was
the search for the self.

154
00:16:43,890 --> 00:16:47,440
Melville could be considered
a pre-existentialist.

155
00:16:50,640 --> 00:16:56,720
You can't deny the whale could be
the search for truth which has been
a theme throughout his whole oeuvre.

156
00:17:01,520 --> 00:17:07,630
You can't overlook the fact that it
is a whale which was the biggest
industry in the 19th century.

157
00:17:07,730 --> 00:17:11,320
The oil was used in lamps,
soaps and even cosmetics.

158
