But I digress! (SOBS)

162
00:17:29,800 --> 00:17:34,880
Wow! Nine places.
That's gotta be a record.

163
00:17:36,600 --> 00:17:42,710
OK, on to new business. This
Friday Principal Littledove will
be dropping by for an evaluation.

164
00:17:42,810 --> 00:17:48,030
I think he'll be very impressed with
what he sees. I don't think he'll
understand it

165
00:17:48,130 --> 00:17:53,350
but his tiny brain will have the dim
perception of the progress you can
make

166
00:17:53,450 --> 00:17:56,470
when students are properly
motivated. (SOBS)

167
00:17:56,570 --> 00:18:00,600
Now, who would like to sink their
teeth into some Bernoulli equations?

168
00:18:05,400 --> 00:18:10,990
Come on, guys. If we don't let the
rankings get to us they mean nothing!

169
00:18:11,090 --> 00:18:13,430
Easy for you to
say, number one.

170
00:18:13,530 --> 00:18:16,310
I have a name!
We all have names!

171
00:18:16,410 --> 00:18:20,310
Oh, my God! I can't
remember mine! This is ridiculous!

172
00:18:20,410 --> 00:18:25,870
School used to be the one place
where you were happy and Herkabe
has taken that away from you.

173
00:18:25,970 --> 00:18:31,870
That stupid board is ruining our
lives! We can't let him do that!
What choice... do we have?

174
00:18:31,970 --> 00:18:35,830
We have the choice that
people have had for centuries.

175
00:18:35,930 --> 00:18:39,350
