Sorry.
I'm sorry.

187
00:19:30,970 --> 00:19:35,830
I tried. My hand
wouldn't let me.

188
00:19:35,930 --> 00:19:39,270
I regret... nothing!

189
00:19:39,370 --> 00:19:44,030
